s within\nthe space-time setting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 May 2013 16:12:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 14 Sep 2013 18:21:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-17"}
