sotropies. An inner\nsmall bar forms, and an end-on view gets closer to fitting the central\ndispersion profile without the need for a central BH, while adding a black hole\nof 2.5 10^9 Msun, in line with the prediction from scaling relations, allows to\nfit the dispersion peak and h3 profiles. EDITED and ABRIDGED.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 May 2013 20:34:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
